RaidSkill.Desc: Enemies who have had their Maximum HP reduced by 50% or more due to Compulsion will be inflicted with until their Compulsion is completely removed.

Raid.Name: Kurokage
Raid.Profile:
The Phantom Fables, guarded and passed down by Allied Hyakkiyako Academy since ancient times, have been exposed to the public.

Could Myouki Kurokage, said to bring about chaos and ruin festivals, be real? Or is it simply a terrible ghost story created by someone with malicious motives? The truth is unknown, but it's time to put an end to this urban legend before it's too late.

RaidSkill.Name: Celadon Flower Divination

RaidSkill.Desc: When ATG gauge is full, deals 750% damage to enemies in a straight line.

RaidSkill.Name: Discharged Explosive
RaidSkill.Desc: When ATG gauge is full, launches a missile that targets the furthest enemy away and deals 750% damage on contact. The missile can be blocked by other students, summons or cover.

RaidSkill.Desc: Every 60s, gains one level of the following effect (max. level 3). Increases by 30%/60%/90%, by 35%/70%/105% and ATG Recovery by 15%/30%/80%, but increases by 10%/20%/50% at level 1/2/3.

RaidSkill.Name: Blaze Rocket
RaidSkill.Desc: Deals 250% damage to up to 2 enemies.

RaidSkill.Name: At This Point...!
RaidSkill.Desc:
When ATG is full, the hovercraft enters Missile Frenzy mode and begins targeting the resort. During Missile Frenzy, the hovercraft is <s:Immortal>.
After Missile Frenzy ends, fills the hovercraft's groggy gauge to the maximum. While the hovercraft is groggy, increases <d:DamagedRatio> by 200% and decreases <d:CriticalChanceResistPoint> by 100%. If the resort is destroyed, the battle is immediately lost.

RaidSkill.Name: Ampoule Missile
RaidSkill.Desc: Deals 450% damage to enemies in a circular area. If this missile is destroyed, increases all students' by 400.

RaidSkill.Name: Shark Missile
RaidSkill.Desc: Deals 450% damage to enemies in a circular area. If this missile is destroyed, deals 999,999 to all other missiles in a circular area.

RaidSkill.Desc: Deals 1000% damage to enemies in a circular area. If this missile is destroyed, deals 400% damage to all other missiles in a circular area.

RaidSkill.Desc: Deals 450% damage to enemies in a circular area. If this missile is destroyed, deals 400% damage to all other missiles in a circular area.

RaidSkill.Name: Riding Grenade
RaidSkill.Desc: Deals 350% damage to one enemy and 550% damage to enemies in a circular area.

Phrenapates: Deals 6000% damage to enemies in a donut-shaped area. During this skill, CC effects inflicted will fill Phrenapates' CC gauge proportional to the duration of the effect. When the gauge reaches an amount equivalent to 4.5s, interrupts Phrenapates skill and increases the of all enemies by 100% for 17s.

RaidSkill.Desc: Shiroko Terror and Phrenapates simulataneously use their skills. Shiroko Terror: Deals 2500% damage to enemies in a donut-shaped area. When the gauge reaches an amount equivalent to 4.5s, interrupts Phrenapates skill and increases the of all enemies by 100% for 17s.

RaidSkill.Desc:
Calls lightning to deal 475% damage to all enemies and summon a red lightning orb.
- The orb can only be targeted by EX Skills and deals 45% damage to nearby enemies.
- If the orb is destroyed, increases the <b:DamageRatio> of enemies in a circular area by 30% for 35s.
- If the orb reaches the Fury of Set, it will significantly increase the lightning gauge.

Absorbs surrounding electricity, dealing 390% damage to all enemies except obelisks.

RaidSkill.Desc:
When ATG is full, throws a lightning spear that deals 410% damage to all enemies.
Completely fills groggy gauge after activation.

RaidSkill.Name: 鷹を射抜く閃光
RaidSkill.Desc:
Lightning strikes will occur periodically. Deals 35% damage to the obelisk with the highest HP and enemies in a circular area around it, and decreases their <d:DamageRatio> by 70% for 40s.
- Lightning strikes deal an additional 200% damage to obelisks.
- The targeted obelisk will enter an <s:EN0008_Obelisk> state until its HP is fully restored, preventing it from being targeted by further lightning strikes.
- If both obelisks are <s:EN0008_Obelisk> the enemy with the highest HP will be targeted by lightning strikes instead.
- Obelisks' HP can only be restored using EX Skills.
(This skill's damage is unaffected by the skill "黎明を喰らう暴風")

Less than 33%: <d:DamageRatio> decreased by 70%.
66% or more: <b:DamageRatio> increased by 80%.
